Class Attribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • graphlib.AttributeOwner
      • graphlib.Attribute
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AttributeComposite, AttributeFloat, AttributeInt, AttributeString

    public abstract class Attribute
extends AttributeOwner
    An abstract attribute class, it has name, context and type attribute, but does not have value. Their descendants extends it with a specific value type.
